# Bug: undefined task-dependency diagnostics underline the whole task.
#
# `analysis/diagnostics.go:undefinedDependencies` anchors on the
# containing task's Position, which spans the entire `task ship`
# block. The dep token "missing" is right there in the source —
# the LSP layer should narrow to it, the same way unresolved-
# variable diagnostics now do.
#
# Expected: underline covers just the word "missing".
# Actual: the entire `task ship { ... }` block underlines.

task build {
    echo building
}

task ship => build, missing {
    echo shipping
}
